`a ‚â´ f ‚â´ b ‚â´ g ‚â´ c = a' ‚â´ f ‚â´ b' ‚â´ g ‚â´ c'`
where `a = a'`, `b = b'`, and `c = c'` can be proved using `pure_coherence`.

